{"tid":2269033,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"144議員轟懲教借疫阻探訪","createTime":"2020-11-03T08:16:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T08:16:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a62c187625e4e03aab9a664a6f0d46eeb1032460","tid":2269033,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T08:16:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201103/TZLBLFFR45BJNCCXQRGH3KMA2E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201103%2FTZLBLFFR45BJNCCXQRGH3KMA2E%2F&d=AZYGjn5ll7vy7cK20AVbo6GvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=d8bb115f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201103%2FTZLBLFFR45BJNCCXQRGH3KMA2E%2F&h=70000f2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201103/TZLBLFFR45BJNCCXQRGH3KMA2E/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n144議員轟懲教借疫阻探訪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/g9mz7s1Bi0erAYGoVDnGaY7fXRQ=/1385x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/POV23TKTF5DTXMP2XLFOYD435I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fg9mz7s1Bi0erAYGoVDnGaY7fXRQ%3D%2F1385x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPOV23TKTF5DTXMP2XLFOYD435I.jpg&h=0245aeb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■邵家臻發起議員聯署促懲教署放寬公務探訪安排。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】懲教署7月中起以抗疫為由，暫停所有議員的公務探訪，即使期間疫情一度放緩，暫停探訪的安排仍無放寬。144名立法會及區議會議員昨日聯署，投訴懲教署阻撓探訪，令在囚人士的求助個案不斷累積，有違囚友申訴的權利。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n斥有政治目的<br />\n<br />\n19名民主派立法會議員與接近全港三分一區議員，昨日聯署去信政務司司長張建宗，投訴懲教署由7月20日起至今阻撓議員的公務探訪申請。聯署發起人、議員邵家臻上載信件至社交網頁，內容指懲教署以減少進入懲教院所的人流以避免疫症流入院所為由，一直暫停公務探訪申請；惟至疫情緩和，甚至政府亦多次放寬防疫措施，懲教署仍並無放寬有關安排。<br />\n<br />\n聯署信指，議員明白要保障囚友與署方人員健康，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n邵家臻指懲教署過去三個月針對民主派議員暫停探訪，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n懲教署昨未有回應何時恢復公務探訪，僅回覆指因疫情反覆，仍維持暫停所有於公務探訪室內進行的非緊急情況的公務探訪，又指會按情況安排在親友探訪室進行有緊急需要的公務探訪。公務探訪須事先申請，可讓探訪者在沒有署方職員的監視下執行公務，此類探訪過往不設時間及次數限制。署方網頁至今仍開放公務探訪的網上申請系統，但列明非緊急及非必要的公務探訪暫停。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/UpbGIm6MFMkLGBSTnOD5OBKMqB8=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Z27L47SHHFDN3EMZKRUEZGA47Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FUpbGIm6MFMkLGBSTnOD5OBKMqB8%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZ27L47SHHFDN3EMZKRUEZGA47Y.jpg&h=7f6e0997&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n邵家臻"}]}